               <msContents>
                  <summary>Notification to a bank to accept a payment owing to Apollonios from Phareitis and Dionysios, holders of the lease of the bath at Philadelphia; underneath there is a note concerning a payment from the oikonomos which has no connection with the "diagraphe" above</summary>
                  <msItem>
                     <note type="general">Written along the fibers with 15 lines; the back is blank</note>
                     <note type="general">There are no marks of creases; this is a draft, never sent</note>
                     <note type="general">The last 4 lines represent a notation separated from the rest by a blank space; they are probably written by a different hand at a later time</note>
                     <textLang mainLang="grc">In Greek</textLang>
